text: Kasibelinurus (meaning "sibling of dart tail") is a genus of Horseshoe crab relative from the Devonian. == Related pages == Patesia - genus of horseshoe crabs misidentified as a part of Kasibelinurus Houia - genus of dekatriatan misidentified as a part of Kasibelinurus == References == Category:Chelicerata Category:Devonian Category:Fossils
title: Kasibelinurus
